This paper deals with the application of a quantum annealer to sample from a Restricted Boltzmann Machine, which is a type of probabilistic graphical model commonly used in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.ET (Emerging Technologies), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
